Woohoo! Great job. Off to check out that Yeah Girl video.

Oh boy. I certainly wouldn’t mind being 30 pounds lighter right now & if I could run 5 miles at a time with ease I’d be thrilled:)

Be grateful for what you have. Working out 6 days / week is hard right now so I might cherish that & dream about the warmer days so I can ride my bike.

Pity some people don’t have food on the table or shoes on feet.
